      content7:
        ' A - user accounts.  In order to use most aspects of the services provided on the Scraapy Platform website and application, you must register in order to obtain and maintain an effective personal account for user services (the "Account"). You must be at least 18 years of age or of legal age in your country (if different from 18) in order to obtain an account. Registering an account requires providing specific personal information to a Scraapy Platform site and an app such as your name, address, mobile phone number, age, and bank account number, as well as at least one valid payment method (either a credit card or an acceptable payment partner). For your part, you agree to write down and maintain accurate, complete, and up-to-date information in your own account. Failure to maintain accurate, complete, and up-to-date information in your account, including the appointment of an invalid or expired payment method, may result in you not being able to access or use the services or terminating the Scraapy Platform website and application of these terms with you. So, you are responsible for all activities conducted in the name of your account, and You also agree to keep your account username and password secure and confidential at all times. You are not entitled to own more than one account unless you are allowed to manage a site and application (Scraapy Platform) writing otherwise. B- User requirements and behavior. The user of the Website and Application (Scraapy Platform) undertakes that he has no legal or security precedents and whoever violates this is fully responsible and the legal consequences of this violation and does not bear any legal liability for the admin of the site and application (Scraapy Platform) and BAHED IT Solutions company, the service is not available for use by persons under the age of 18. You are not entitled to authorize the use of your account to third parties, nor can you allow people under the age of 18 to obtain services from the Scraapy Platform website and application unless they are with you, and you may not waive your account or transfer ownership to any other person or entity and agree on your part to comply with all applicable laws when using the Scraapy Platform website and application and you may only use it for legal purposes and, when you use Scraapy Platform website and application, may not cause Harm, inconvenience, harassment or property damage, whether to the admin of Scraapy Platform site and application or any other parties. In some cases, you may be asked to provide personal proof of access or use of services and agree that they may be denied access to or use of services if you refuse to provide proof of personal identity. Scraapy offers the following services: •Client Page, and get a portfolio. •Buy and sell all types of Hazardous and Non-Hazardous recyclable waste, Disposed waste. •Request for services. •Purchase products. •Request for short/long-term materials supply contracts. •Enjoy the benefits of your subscription package and take advantage of the offers •Live Chat with Scraapy team.',
      heading8: 'Text messages.',
